{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_05_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 3話 お兄ちゃんのイジワル～！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん。仕事の合間を縫っての勉強方法なんだけど\n沙季にも聞いてみたんだ。良かったら参考にしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san‚ I asked Saki about studying in between work.\nIf you'd like‚ you can take it as a reference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季さんからですか！　最近お互い忙しくてゆっくり\nお話し出来てなかったから……とっても嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From Saki-san! We've been so busy lately that\nwe haven't had a chance to talk properly… I'm really happy about this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ……\n『新幹線での移動中に暗記ものの時間を設ける』ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ hmm…\n\"Set aside time for memorization during Shinkansen rides‚\" is that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.533333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 17.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "『台本を読み込んでいると聞いたので、気分転換くらい\nの軽い気持ちで暗記をするのもアリだと思います』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Since I heard you're reading scripts‚\nit might be worth trying to memorize them as a light distraction.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……こういうやり方もあるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So there's a method like this too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にいた頃、沙季は東京までの往復時間を利用して\n読書や暗記ものの勉強をしていたらしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Saki was in Hoshimi City‚ she used the round trip time to Tokyo\nfor reading and memorization.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "沙季さんが実際にやっていたなら\nとっても説得力がありますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Saki-san actually did it‚\nit's very convincing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "今までは台本だけずっと読み込んでたり\n数学の問題を解いたりしてたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until now‚ I've been just reading scripts or\nsolving math problems…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "テストまであと何回か新幹線移動があるので\n早速試してみますね。ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are a few more Shinkansen rides before the test‚\nso I'll try it out right away. Thank you very much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――定期テスト最終日＆撮影当日の午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Last day of the exam & Shooting day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん、もうじき来るはずだけど……\nあ、奥山さん！　テストはどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san‚ she should be here soon…\nAh‚ Okuyama-san! How was the test?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.666666700007,
          "startTime": 76.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……今回の定期テストの手応えは～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… The feeling I got from this term's test is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "ブイ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "V for Victory!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……！　これで撮影も安心して送り出せるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's great…! Now I can send you off for the shoot with peace of mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、いっぱい協力してくれて\n本当にありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you so much for your help.\nI really appreciate it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "これで悩みもすっかりなくなりましたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that all my worries are gone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "見てて下さいね、今日の撮影は\nとびっきりいい感じにしてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please watch‚ today's shoot will be\nabsolutely fantastic!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　お花畑がとっても綺麗です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…! The flower field is so beautiful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ドレスも素敵で……\nまるでおとぎの国に迷い込んだみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The dress is also lovely…\nIt's like I've wandered into a fairytale kingdom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……？　なるほど\nまずは自由にはしゃいでほしい……ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? I see.\nFirst‚ you want me to have fun freely… Is that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、それなら遊んじゃいますね！\nカメラマンさん、頑張ってついて来て下さ～い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood‚ then I'll have a blast!\nPhotographer‚ please keep up with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん、凄くのびのびとしてるな……\nスタッフさん達も自然と笑顔になってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san‚ you're so full of energy…\nThe staff members are naturally smiling too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、いい香り！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ it smells so nice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "静かに花を眺めるのも楽しいし\n音楽を聴きながらお散歩もしてみたいなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's enjoyable to quietly gaze at the flowers‚\nor to take a leisurely walk while listening to music.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "……ふう！　はしゃぎ過ぎちゃいました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew! I got a bit carried away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "これくらいがちょうどいいですか？　そう言って\nもらえると嬉しいです、ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this about right? If you say so‚\nI'd be happy to receive that. Thank you very much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "よしよし、いい感じだぞ",
      "translations": {
